    { title: "Crews show up to the wrong job", description: "Schedules change, customers reschedule, materials run late — but the office can't push updates to the truck in real time." },
    { title: "Job cost is a guess until close-out", description: "Materials, labor, change orders and supplier invoices live in spreadsheets that get reconciled weeks after the job ships." },
    { title: "No visibility into which reps actually close", description: "You can't see who is producing, what's stuck in proposal, or which neighborhoods convert — so coaching and ad spend are blind." },
    { title: "Customers forget you exist after close", description: "No automated maintenance follow-up, no review ask, no referral nurture — and that's where most repeat revenue gets left." },
